&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;beagleboard-weekly-gsoc-office-hour&quot;&gt;BeagleBoard Weekly GSoC Office Hour&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#beagleboard-weekly-gsoc-office-hour&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: beagleboard-weekly-gsoc-office-hour&quot; style=&quot;visibility: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All meetings officially take place on the &lt;strong&gt;Beagleboard Discord channel&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;, scheduled every &lt;strong&gt;Thursday at 15:30 UTC&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All contributors are expected to:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be available during this time for weekly check-ins on blockers and significant progress.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inform the team &lt;strong&gt;in advance&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; if unable to attend.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit weekly reports &lt;strong&gt;well ahead of time&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
