&lt;h2 id=&quot;hardware-update&quot;&gt;Hardware Update&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#hardware-update&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: hardware-update&quot; style=&quot;visibility: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
