&lt;p&gt;I received my development hardware from &lt;strong&gt;Beagleboard.org&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; on &lt;strong&gt;May 26th, 2025&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;.
Special thanks to &lt;strong&gt;@lorforlinux&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; for coordinating the shipment.
The BELA Cape is expected to arrive a bit later, as it was recently restocked. I’ll proceed with setup and testing as soon as it arrives.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
